S.FORM: == saungay nu binawlan-20170923 sapicudad a laylay nu mapalaway == tatukian 2016 mihca 9 bulad 23 demiad (sakaenem a demiad nu lipay) puenengan Tiway Sayiun kalisiw tapang a saupuan, Kalingku Kuomin sakacacay cie 53 siang 1 banggu sakamuay : Tuku Sayiun tayni mitengilay: Sakizaya mapalaway, Sakizaya patuduay, Lubas-kuwansaedap lacul Wiki-sapisulit tu mapalaway a nazipa'an u simsim nu mabelecay nu Sakizaya siwkay ni Dungy-Dietu sakaizaway nu epah i lisin u pakan nu diedietuway malialac baluinana u likisi nu Palamal natayniay ci Balucu' sasaydang,Su Yi Ru sasaydang, Dungy Sela mapalaway, Lin Xing Yu mapalaway, Lisin Cudad mapalaway, Dawa Kukuy patuduay, Lin Meilling patuduay, Uul Balaw patuduay, Balah Huisin, Kulihusin Sayiun, Li Chunlan atu wawa niza. muazih tu tatengaay belih nu Hulam a kumu Panan,蘇羿如博士Simpi Adingu,嚴苡嘉祭師Dungy Sela, Lisin Cudad,巫曉涵祝禱司Dawa Kukuy,林美玲祝禱司Abas Kucya,歐沃兒法荖祝禱司Uul Balaw, Tuku Balaw,督固撒耘Tuku Sayun,耕莘撒耘Kulihuysin Sayun,飛亞飛丞Balah Huysin,李春蘭母子3人

== saongay no binawlan-20170923 sapicodad a laylay no mapalaway == tatokian 2016 mihca 9 bolad 23 demiad (sakaenem a demiad no lipay) poenengan Tiway Sayion kalisiw tapang a saopoan, Kalingko Koomin sakacacay cie 53 siang 1 banggo sakamoay : Toko Sayion tayni mitengilay: Sakizaya mapalaway, Sakizaya patodoay, Lobas-kowansaedap lacol Wiki-sapisolit to mapalaway a nazipa'an o simsim no mabelecay no Sakizaya siwkay ni Dongy-Dieto sakaizaway no epah i lisin o pakan no diedietoway malialac baloinana o likisi no Palamal natayniay ci Baloco' sasaydang,So Yi Ro sasaydang, Dongy Sela mapalaway, Lin Xing Yo mapalaway, Lisin Codad mapalaway, Dawa Kokoy patodoay, Lin Meilling patodoay, Uol Balaw patodoay, Balah Hoisin, Kolihosin Sayion, Li Chonlan ato wawa niza. moazih to tatengaay belih no Holam a komo Panan,蘇羿如博士Simpi Adingo,嚴苡嘉祭師Dongy Sela, Lisin Codad,巫曉涵祝禱司Dawa Kokoy,林美玲祝禱司Abas Kocya,歐沃兒法荖祝禱司Uol Balaw, Toko Balaw,督固撒耘Toko Sayon,耕莘撒耘Kolihoysin Sayon,飛亞飛丞Balah Hoysin,李春蘭母子3人
